  "body": "### Metadata\r\n\r\n* **Hardfork**: all of 'em\r\n\r\n### What was wrong?\r\n\r\nThe modular exponentiation precompile doesn't pad its input value to the correct length before slicing it up, so each array access can `IndexError` incorrectly.\r\n\r\n### Sources\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/cb7f35996d8f8dfd44172b72cbb08829a33db527/core/vm/contracts.go#L365\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/cb7f35996d8f8dfd44172b72cbb08829a33db527/core/vm/common.go#L54\r\n",
